  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the specificity of the cobas TaqScreen MPX Test for the simultaneous
      detection of HBV DNA, HCV RNA and HIV-1 Group M in a minimum of 100,000 individual donor
      samples in 96-unit pools.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
